Package: DEDML
Type: Package
Title: Donor-Blocked Double Machine Learning for Single-Cell Differential Expression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Yuxin", family = "Yin", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "yyin0906@gmail.com")
    )
Description: Implements a donor-blocked double machine learning pipeline for
    single-cell differential expression with pseudobulk residual regression.
    Users can choose dataset-specific treatment and outcome confounders,
    select treatment and outcome learners, and run the full workflow through
    package functions instead of ad-hoc scripts.
